{
    "esm": "0.4.0",
    "metadata": {
        "name": "CloudPhysics",
        "description": "Composed cloud microphysics model (Seinfeld & Pandis 2006, Ch. 17). Flat composition of CloudDynamics (adiabatic thermodynamics, LCL height), IcePhysics (freezing point depression, ice nuclei), RainFormation (collision-coalescence, raindrop spectra), and AerosolScavenging (scavenging ratios and coefficient). Shared physical constants M_w and R unify CloudDynamics and IcePhysics. Ice particle diameter (D_p_ice) and collector drop diameter (D_p_rain) are kept as independent parameters. Migrated from Aerosol.jl src/cloud_physics.jl:735 (esm-c8z).",
        "tags": [
            "aerosol",
            "cloud_physics",
            "thermodynamics",
            "ice_physics",
            "rain_formation",
            "aerosol_scavenging",
            "seinfeld_pandis"
        ]
    },
    "models": {
        "CloudPhysics": {
            "reference": {
                "citation": "Seinfeld, J. H. and Pandis, S. N. (2006). Atmospheric Chemistry and Physics: From Air Pollution to Climate Change, 2nd Edition, John Wiley & Sons, Chapter 17.",
                "notes": "source_ref: Aerosol.jl@c8c640bb636b22f2425460e9ed5cba50793bfee1:src/cloud_physics.jl:735\n\nUpstream CloudPhysics is an MTK @component that calls EarthSciML coupling.couple() on four sub-components: CloudDynamics, IcePhysics, RainFormation, and AerosolScavenging. The couple() call unifies shared parameter names across components — specifically M_w (molecular weight of water) and R (universal gas constant), which appear in both CloudDynamics and IcePhysics with identical values.\n\nThis ESM flattens all four sub-models into a single model following the same pattern as aerosol_dynamics.esm:\n- CloudDynamics: pure-algebraic observed variables (Γ_d, p_sat, w_vs, T_d, h_LCL). Temperature T_0 (default 293.15 K) is the surface/parcel temperature for the LCL calculation.\n- IcePhysics: algebraic state equations (ΔT_f, T_e, kelvin_ice, IN). Temperature T (default 263.15 K) is the ice-phase temperature, kept separate from T_0 as in the upstream composition.\n- RainFormation: algebraic state equations (E_t, dm_dt, F_dist, n_MP). The upstream D_p parameter (collector drop diameter) is renamed D_p_rain to avoid collision with IcePhysics.\n- AerosolScavenging: algebraic state equations (F_mass, F_number, Λ). No parameter conflicts.\n\nName collision resolution: Both IcePhysics and RainFormation have a parameter named D_p (units m) but with distinct physical meanings and order-of-magnitude different defaults (1e-6 m for ice particles vs 1e-3 m for rain collector drops). In the upstream MTK system these are namespaced as ice.D_p and rain.D_p. In this flat ESM they are D_p_ice (ice particle diameter) and D_p_rain (collector drop diameter) respectively. All equation expression trees are updated accordingly.\n\nShared parameters M_w and R are listed once and referenced by both the CloudDynamics observed-variable expressions and the IcePhysics equations.\n\nThe coupling.couple feature in the upstream code produces no inter-model ODE coupling for this composition — the four sub-models are thermodynamically related (common M_w, R, and conceptually related T_0/T) but their outputs do not feed into each other's equations. The composition is primarily a convenience wrapper for downstream coupled atmospheric models.\n\nTolerance (rel=1e-8, abs=1e-12): all outputs are time-independent algebraic quantities. Inherits the strictest per-assertion tolerance needed across the four sub-models. CloudDynamics observed variables use pure closed-form expressions; 1e-8 easily covers float64 roundoff. The abs=1e-12 floor handles the molality=0 (ΔT_f=0) boundary."
            },
            "tolerance": {
                "rel": 1.0e-8,
                "abs": 1.0e-12
            },
            "variables": {
                "M_w": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "kg/mol",
                    "default": 0.018015,
                    "description": "Molecular weight of water. Shared between CloudDynamics (w_vs, T_d) and IcePhysics (T_e, kelvin_ice)."
                },
                "R": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "J/(mol*K)",
                    "default": 8.314,
                    "description": "Universal gas constant. Shared between CloudDynamics (T_d) and IcePhysics (T_e, kelvin_ice)."
                },
                "M_a": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "kg/mol",
                    "default": 0.02897,
                    "description": "Molecular weight of dry air (CloudDynamics)."
                },
                "g": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m/s^2",
                    "default": 9.81,
                    "description": "Gravitational acceleration (CloudDynamics)."
                },
                "c_p_air": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "J/(kg*K)",
                    "default": 1005.0,
                    "description": "Specific heat of air at constant pressure (CloudDynamics)."
                },
                "p_sat_ref": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "Pa",
                    "default": 610.94,
                    "description": "Magnus formula reference saturation pressure at 0°C (CloudDynamics)."
                },
                "magnus_a": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 17.625,
                    "description": "Magnus formula coefficient a (CloudDynamics)."
                },
                "T_magnus_offset": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K",
                    "default": 273.15,
                    "description": "Magnus formula temperature offset 0°C in Kelvin (CloudDynamics)."
                },
                "magnus_b": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K",
                    "default": 243.04,
                    "description": "Magnus formula coefficient b (CloudDynamics)."
                },
                "T_0": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K",
                    "default": 293.15,
                    "description": "Surface/parcel temperature for adiabatic cloud-base thermodynamics (CloudDynamics). Distinct from the ice-phase temperature T."
                },
                "RH": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 0.8,
                    "description": "Relative humidity (dimensionless, 0–1) for LCL calculation (CloudDynamics)."
                },
                "p_a": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "Pa",
                    "default": 101325.0,
                    "description": "Atmospheric pressure (CloudDynamics)."
                },
                "ΔH_v": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "J/kg",
                    "default": 2500000.0,
                    "description": "Latent heat of vaporization (CloudDynamics, S&P Table 17.1)."
                },
                "Γ_d": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "K/m",
                    "description": "Dry adiabatic lapse rate Γ_d = g/c_p_air (CloudDynamics, Eq. 17.44). Constant ≈ 9.76 K/km.",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": ["g", "c_p_air"]
                    }
                },
                "p_sat": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "Pa",
                    "description": "Saturation vapor pressure at T_0 via Magnus formula (CloudDynamics). p_sat ≈ 2333 Pa at 20°C.",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "*",
                        "args": [
                            "p_sat_ref",
                            {
                                "op": "exp",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "/",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": [
                                                    "magnus_a",
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "+",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            "T_0",
                                                            {"op": "*", "args": [-1, "T_magnus_offset"]}
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "op": "+",
                                                "args": [
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "+",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            "T_0",
                                                            {"op": "*", "args": [-1, "T_magnus_offset"]}
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "magnus_b"
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "w_vs": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Saturation water vapor mixing ratio w_vs = M_w p_sat / (M_a p_a) (CloudDynamics, Eq. 17.46).",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            {"op": "*", "args": ["M_w", "p_sat"]},
                            {"op": "*", "args": ["M_a", "p_a"]}
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "T_d": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "K",
                    "description": "Dew-point temperature T_d = T_0 + (R T_0² / (ΔH_v M_w)) ln(RH) (CloudDynamics, Eq. 17.43).",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "+",
                        "args": [
                            "T_0",
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "/",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": ["R", {"op": "^", "args": ["T_0", 2]}]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": ["ΔH_v", "M_w"]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {"op": "log", "args": ["RH"]}
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "h_LCL": {
                    "type": "observed",
                    "units": "m",
                    "description": "Lifting condensation level height h_LCL = (T_0 - T_d) / Γ_d (CloudDynamics, Eq. 17.49).",
                    "expression": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "+",
                                "args": ["T_0", {"op": "*", "args": [-1, "T_d"]}]
                            },
                            "Γ_d"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "ρ_i": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "kg/m^3",
                    "default": 917.0,
                    "description": "Density of ice (IcePhysics)."
                },
                "T_freeze": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K",
                    "default": 273.15,
                    "description": "Freezing point of pure water (IcePhysics)."
                },
                "ΔH_m_mass": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "J/kg",
                    "default": 333500.0,
                    "description": "Latent heat of fusion of water (IcePhysics)."
                },
                "K_f": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K*kg/mol",
                    "default": 1.86,
                    "description": "Cryoscopic constant of water (IcePhysics)."
                },
                "IN_ref": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/m^3",
                    "default": 1000.0,
                    "description": "Ice nuclei reference concentration at T_IN_ref (IcePhysics, Eq. 17.103)."
                },
                "IN_coeff": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/K",
                    "default": 0.6,
                    "description": "Ice nuclei exponential temperature coefficient (IcePhysics, Eq. 17.103)."
                },
                "T_IN_ref": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K",
                    "default": 253.0,
                    "description": "Reference temperature for ice nuclei parameterization (IcePhysics)."
                },
                "dim_eps": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 1.0e-30,
                    "description": "Small value added to water activity to prevent log(0) (IcePhysics)."
                },
                "T": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K",
                    "default": 263.15,
                    "description": "Ice-phase temperature (IcePhysics). Separate from T_0 (cloud-dynamics surface temperature)."
                },
                "σ_ia": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "N/m",
                    "default": 0.106,
                    "description": "Ice-air surface tension (IcePhysics, Eq. 17.102)."
                },
                "D_p_ice": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 1.0e-6,
                    "description": "Ice particle diameter (IcePhysics, Eq. 17.102). Renamed from D_p to avoid collision with D_p_rain (collector drop diameter) in RainFormation."
                },
                "a_w": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 1.0,
                    "description": "Water activity (IcePhysics, Eq. 17.101)."
                },
                "molality": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "mol/kg",
                    "default": 0.0,
                    "description": "Solute molality of the solution (IcePhysics, Eq. 17.100)."
                },
                "ΔT_f": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "K",
                    "description": "Freezing point depression ΔT_f = K_f * molality (IcePhysics, Eq. 17.100)."
                },
                "T_e": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "K",
                    "description": "Equilibrium freezing temperature from water activity (IcePhysics, Eq. 17.101)."
                },
                "kelvin_ice": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Kelvin curvature factor for ice particle vapor pressure (IcePhysics, Eq. 17.102). Always > 1."
                },
                "IN": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1/m^3",
                    "description": "Ice nuclei concentration (IcePhysics, Eq. 17.103)."
                },
                "π_val": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 3.141592653589793,
                    "description": "Pi (RainFormation)."
                },
                "F_diam_ref": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 1.3e-3,
                    "description": "Best distribution diameter scale (RainFormation, Eq. 17.107: 1.3 mm)."
                },
                "F_exp": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 2.25,
                    "description": "Best distribution exponent (RainFormation, Eq. 17.107)."
                },
                "one": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 1.0,
                    "description": "Unity constant for F_dist expression (RainFormation)."
                },
                "p0_unit": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "mm/hr",
                    "default": 1.0,
                    "description": "Unit rainfall intensity for nondimensionalization (RainFormation)."
                },
                "D_p_rain": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 1.0e-3,
                    "description": "Collector drop diameter (RainFormation). Renamed from D_p to avoid collision with D_p_ice (ice particle diameter) in IcePhysics."
                },
                "d_p": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m",
                    "default": 1.0e-5,
                    "description": "Collected droplet diameter (RainFormation, Eq. 17.106)."
                },
                "E_coll": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 0.5,
                    "description": "Collision efficiency (RainFormation, Eq. 17.104)."
                },
                "E_coal": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 1.0,
                    "description": "Coalescence efficiency (RainFormation, Eq. 17.105)."
                },
                "w_L": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 1.0e-3,
                    "description": "Liquid water mass mixing ratio kg/kg (RainFormation, Eq. 17.106)."
                },
                "v_D": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m/s",
                    "default": 5.0,
                    "description": "Fall velocity of collector drop (RainFormation, Eq. 17.106)."
                },
                "v_d": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m/s",
                    "default": 0.01,
                    "description": "Fall velocity of collected droplet (RainFormation, Eq. 17.106)."
                },
                "ρ_a": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "kg/m^3",
                    "default": 1.225,
                    "description": "Air density (RainFormation, Eq. 17.106)."
                },
                "p_0": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "mm/hr",
                    "default": 1.0,
                    "description": "Rainfall intensity (RainFormation, Eq. 17.107)."
                },
                "n_0": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/m^4",
                    "default": 8.0e6,
                    "description": "Marshall-Palmer intercept parameter (RainFormation, Eq. 17.108: 8000 m⁻³ mm⁻¹)."
                },
                "ψ": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/m",
                    "default": 4100.0,
                    "description": "Marshall-Palmer slope parameter (RainFormation, Eq. 17.108)."
                },
                "E_t": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Collection efficiency E_t = E_coll * E_coal (RainFormation, Eq. 17.106)."
                },
                "dm_dt": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "kg/s",
                    "description": "Mass accretion rate by continuous collection (RainFormation, Eq. 17.106)."
                },
                "F_dist": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Best raindrop size CDF (RainFormation, Eq. 17.107)."
                },
                "n_MP": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1/m^4",
                    "description": "Marshall-Palmer raindrop number density (RainFormation, Eq. 17.108)."
                },
                "C_0": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/m^3",
                    "default": 1.0e9,
                    "description": "Initial aerosol mass concentration (AerosolScavenging, Eq. 17.84)."
                },
                "C_int": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/m^3",
                    "default": 5.0e8,
                    "description": "Interstitial aerosol mass concentration (AerosolScavenging, Eq. 17.84)."
                },
                "N_0": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/m^3",
                    "default": 1.0e9,
                    "description": "Initial aerosol number concentration (AerosolScavenging, Eq. 17.85)."
                },
                "N_int": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/m^3",
                    "default": 3.0e8,
                    "description": "Interstitial aerosol number concentration (AerosolScavenging, Eq. 17.85)."
                },
                "K_coll": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "m^3/s",
                    "default": 1.0e-12,
                    "description": "Collision coefficient (AerosolScavenging, Eq. 17.92)."
                },
                "N_d": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/m^3",
                    "default": 1.0e8,
                    "description": "Cloud droplet number concentration (AerosolScavenging, Eq. 17.92)."
                },
                "F_mass": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Mass scavenging ratio F_mass = (C_0 - C_int)/C_0 (AerosolScavenging, Eq. 17.84)."
                },
                "F_number": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1",
                    "description": "Number scavenging ratio F_number = (N_0 - N_int)/N_0 (AerosolScavenging, Eq. 17.85)."
                },
                "Λ": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "description": "Scavenging coefficient Λ = N_d * K_coll (AerosolScavenging, Eq. 17.92)."
                }
            },
            "equations": [
                {
                    "lhs": "ΔT_f",
                    "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["K_f", "molality"]}
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "T_e",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "+",
                        "args": [
                            "T_freeze",
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "/",
                                        "args": [
                                            {"op": "*", "args": ["R", {"op": "^", "args": ["T_freeze", 2]}]},
                                            {"op": "*", "args": ["ΔH_m_mass", "M_w"]}
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {"op": "log", "args": [{"op": "+", "args": ["a_w", "dim_eps"]}]}
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "kelvin_ice",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "exp",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "/",
                                "args": [
                                    {"op": "*", "args": [4, "M_w", "σ_ia"]},
                                    {"op": "*", "args": ["R", "T", "ρ_i", "D_p_ice"]}
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "IN",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "*",
                        "args": [
                            "IN_ref",
                            {
                                "op": "exp",
                                "args": [
                                    {
                                        "op": "*",
                                        "args": [
                                            "IN_coeff",
                                            {"op": "+", "args": ["T_IN_ref", {"op": "*", "args": [-1, "T"]}]}
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "E_t",
                    "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["E_coll", "E_coal"]}
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "dm_dt",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "*",
                        "args": [
                            {"op": "/", "args": ["π_val", 4]},
                            "E_t",
                            {"op": "^", "args": [{"op": "+", "args": ["D_p_rain", "d_p"]}, 2]},
                            "w_L",
                            "ρ_a",
                            {"op": "abs", "args": [{"op": "+", "args": ["v_D", {"op": "*", "args": [-1, "v_d"]}]}]}
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "F_dist",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "+",
                        "args": [
                            "one",
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    -1,
                                    {
                                        "op": "exp",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "*",
                                                "args": [
                                                    -1,
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "^",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "/",
                                                                "args": [
                                                                    "D_p_rain",
                                                                    {
                                                                        "op": "*",
                                                                        "args": [
                                                                            "F_diam_ref",
                                                                            {
                                                                                "op": "^",
                                                                                "args": [
                                                                                    {"op": "/", "args": ["p_0", "p0_unit"]},
                                                                                    0.232
                                                                                ]
                                                                            }
                                                                        ]
                                                                    }
                                                                ]
                                                            },
                                                            "F_exp"
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "n_MP",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "*",
                        "args": [
                            "n_0",
                            {"op": "exp", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [-1, "ψ", "D_p_rain"]}]}
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "F_mass",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            {"op": "+", "args": ["C_0", {"op": "*", "args": [-1, "C_int"]}]},
                            "C_0"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "F_number",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            {"op": "+", "args": [{"op": "*", "args": [-1, "N_int"]}, "N_0"]},
                            "N_0"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "lhs": "Λ",
                    "rhs": {"op": "*", "args": ["N_d", "K_coll"]}
                }
            ],
            "tests": [
                {
                    "id": "defaults_all_submodels",
                    "description": "Reference run at upstream Aerosol.jl defaults for all four sub-models simultaneously. Verifies all 13 output variables at t=0 and t=3600 s. All outputs are time-independent algebraic quantities, so values must be identical at both times.\n\nExpected values sourced from cloud_dynamics.esm (Γ_d, p_sat, w_vs, T_d, h_LCL), ice_physics.esm (ΔT_f, T_e, kelvin_ice, IN), rain_formation.esm (E_t, dm_dt, F_dist, n_MP), and aerosol_scavenging.esm (F_mass, F_number, Λ) — each cross-validated against the upstream Aerosol.jl test suite.",
                    "time_span": {"start": 0.0, "end": 3600.0},
                    "assertions": [
                        {"variable": "Γ_d",       "time": 0.0,    "expected": 0.009761194029850746},
                        {"variable": "Γ_d",       "time": 3600.0, "expected": 0.009761194029850746},
                        {"variable": "p_sat",      "time": 0.0,    "expected": 2333.4406230993577},
                        {"variable": "p_sat",      "time": 3600.0, "expected": 2333.4406230993577},
                        {"variable": "w_vs",       "time": 0.0,    "expected": 0.014320754941837679},
                        {"variable": "w_vs",       "time": 3600.0, "expected": 0.014320754941837679},
                        {"variable": "T_d",        "time": 0.0,    "expected": 289.6100275457325},
